.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-3::.
There are 7 different nationalities: malaysian, american, argentine, thai, japanese, australian, british
7 different pets are kept: horse, guinea-pig, goldfish, cat, chinchilla, ferret, bird
 1. the japanese is on the left of the malaysian##1
 2. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
 3. the owner of the chinchilla is the british##1
 4. the argentine is on the left of the australian##1
 5. the owner of the horse is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
 6. the thai is the owner of the cat##1
 7. the malaysian is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
 8. the owner of the horse is between the owner of the bird and the thai##2
 9. the malaysian is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1
10. the american is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3     |    4    |   5    |   6    |     7     |
| Nationality   | british | japanese | malaysian | american   | thai | argentine | australian |
| Pet           | chinchilla | ferret     | guinea-pig     | goldfish | cat   | horse   | bird    |

