.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-4::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, 7up, mirinda, hot-chocolate, coffee, milk, soy-milk
There are 7 different nationalities: colombian, egyptian, american, dutch, argentine, russian, canadian
 1. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the american##1
 2. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the argentine##1
 3. the russian is on the right of the dutch##1
 4. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the argentine##1
 5. the colombian is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 6. the dutch is between the person drinking mirinda and the russian##2
 7. the person drinking almond-milk is in the middle##1
 8. the dutch is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 9. the person drinking 7up is the egyptian##1
10. the colombian is the person drinking soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |   4    |     5      |     6     |    7     |
| Beverage      | mirinda    | coffee  | hot-chocolate  | almond-milk  | soy-milk      | milk       | 7up |
| Nationality   | argentine | dutch | russian | canadian | colombian | american | egyptian  |

