.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-5::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: funk, blues, dubstep, hip-hop, trance, salsa, electronic
The people use 7 different means of transport: subway, tram, trike, roller, jet-ski, taxi, bus
1. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
2. the person driving the jet-ski is the fan of blues##1
3. the person driving the subway is between the fan of electronic and the fan of funk##2
4. the fan of salsa is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
5. the person driving the subway is in the middle##1
6. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the fan of funk##1
7. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
8. the person driving the tram is the fan of hip-hop##1
9. the fan of trance is the person driving the taxi##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2   |     3     |  4   |     5     |     6      |  7   |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop      | trance | funk | dubstep | electronic      | blues      | salsa |
| Transport     | tram | taxi | bus       | subway | trike | jet-ski | roller |

