.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-6::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  librarian, teacher, designer, journalist, electrician, dressmaker, nurse
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: cricket, weightlifting, surfing, handball, tennis, golf, volleyball
1. the designer is on the left of the nurse##1
2. the person who's sport is surfing is the electrician##1
3. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the person who's sport is golf##1
4. the teacher is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1
5. the dressmaker is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
6. the person who's sport is volleyball is between the person who's sport is tennis and the librarian##2
7. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
8. the dressmaker is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |      2      |        3        |      4       |     5     |     6     |   7    |
| Job     | electrician | librarian | journalist | dressmaker | teacher | designer     | nurse |
| Sport   | surfing   | handball    | volleyball    | tennis      | weightlifting  | cricket | golf |

