.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-7::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, mirinda, tea, water, juice, 7up, soy-milk
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: badminton, skiing, ice-hockey, handball, sailing, lacrosse, baseball
 1. the person who's sport is lacrosse is the person drinking juice##1
 2. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person who's sport is baseball##1
 3. the person who's sport is skiing is in the middle##1
 4. the person drinking tea is between the person who's sport is sailing and the person who's sport is baseball##2
 5. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the person drinking water##1
 6. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1
 7. the person who's sport is handball is the person drinking almond-milk##1
 8. the person drinking 7up is the person who's sport is sailing##1
 9. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is between the person who's sport is sailing and the person drinking juice##2
10. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |       3       |    4    |    5     |    6    |    7     |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | mirinda    | water | tea   | 7up | soy-milk    | juice |
| Sport      | handball | badminton | baseball    | skiing | sailing    | ice-hockey | lacrosse  |

