.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-8::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: milk, almond-milk, iced-tea, tea, coffee, 7up, soy-milk
The people have 7 different jobs:  project-manager, firefighter, journalist, writer, dancer, videographer, electrician
 1. the dancer is on the left of the writer##1
 2. the project-manager is on the left of the journalist##1
 3. the videographer is on the far left##1
 4. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
 5. the dancer is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 6. the person drinking 7up is between the person drinking tea and the person drinking soy-milk##2
 7. the firefighter is on the right of the videographer##1
 8. the project-manager is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
 9. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
10. the person drinking almond-milk is between the person drinking soy-milk and the person drinking milk##2
11. the dancer is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1        |     2      |      3       |     4     |         5          |     6      |     7     |
| Beverage   | iced-tea  | coffee   | milk         | almond-milk     | soy-milk              | 7up    | tea     |
| Job        | videographer | firefighter | dancer | writer | electrician | project-manager | journalist |

