.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-9::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: comedy, animation, time-travel, martial-arts, scientific, fantasy, sports
The people use 7 different means of transport: scooter, snowmobile, van, bike, airplane, car, subway
1. the person watching comedy movies is the person driving the car##1
2. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the person watching comedy movies##1
3. the person watching scientific movies is between the person driving the subway and the person driving the airplane##2
4. the person watching animation movies is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
5. the person driving the scooter is in the middle##1
6. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
7. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
8. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the person watching fantasy movies##1
9. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |   3    |    4    |    5     |     6     |   7    |
| Movie-Genre   | animation | martial-arts     | fantasy | scientific | time-travel | sports  | comedy |
| Transport     | van | bike | airplane   | scooter     | subway    | snowmobile | car   |

