.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-10::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, almond-milk, soy-milk, lemonade, sprite, water, hot-chocolate
The people have 7 different hobbies: chess, collecting, rock-climbing, card-games, dancing, writing, camping
1. the person who's hobby is writing is the person drinking soy-milk##1
2. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
3. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
4. the person who's hobby is writing is between the person who's hobby is card-games and the person who's hobby is collecting##2
5. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
6. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the far right##1
7. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
8. the person drinking lemonade is between the person drinking sprite and the person who's hobby is writing##2
9. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |      3      |      4       |    5    |      6      |    7    |
| Beverage   | almond-milk  | iced-tea       | hot-chocolate         | sprite         | lemonade   | soy-milk        | water |
| Hobby      | camping | rock-climbing | chess | dancing | collecting | writing | card-games  |

