.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-11::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: traveling, magic-tricks, chess, photography, camping, video-games, drawing
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: parkour, badminton, swimming, surfing, water-polo, cycling, rugby
1. the person who's sport is rugby is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
3. the person who's hobby is camping is in the middle##1
4. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1
5. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the person who's sport is swimming##1
6. the person who's hobby is photography is between the person who's sport is water-polo and the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##2
7. the person who's hobby is video-games is between the person who's hobby is chess and the person who's hobby is drawing##2
8. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left of the person who's sport is surfing##1
9. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left of the person who's hobby is traveling##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |       2       |     3      |       4       |    5    |     6      |       7       |
| Hobby   | drawing | video-games       | chess    | camping | photography | magic-tricks     | traveling       |
| Sport   | badminton    | surfing | cycling | water-polo        | swimming | parkour | rugby |

