.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-12::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: mystery, animation, sports, martial-arts, fantasy, thriller, crime
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: classical, techno, electronic, trance, soul, blues, country
 1. the person watching mystery movies is the fan of country##1
 2. the person watching crime movies is on the left of the fan of soul##1
 3. the person watching mystery movies is between the person watching martial-arts movies and the fan of classical##2
 4. the person watching thriller movies is between the person watching crime movies and the person watching fantasy movies##2
 5. the fan of blues is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
 6. the fan of electronic is on the right of the fan of classical##1
 7. the person watching sports movies is on the far right##1
 8. the person watching sports movies is the fan of soul##1
 9. the fan of trance is on the far left##1
10. the fan of trance is the person watching martial-arts movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3   |   4   |    5    |   6    |   7    |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts | mystery | animation  | fantasy   | thriller | crime | sports |
| Music-Genre   | trance     | country       | classical | electronic | blues  | techno   | soul   |

