 3. the person drinking soy-milk is between the fan of r&b and the person drinking lemonade##2
 4. the person drinking water is between the person drinking coffee and the person drinking lemonade##2
 5. the fan of pop is on the left of the fan of r&b##1
 6. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the fan of hip-hop##1
 7. the fan of pop is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 8. the fan of blues is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
 9. the fan of punk is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
10. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person drinking milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
