 3. the person drinking coffee is the person eating radish##1
 4. the person drinking coffee is on the far left##1
 5. the person eating potato is on the left of the person eating peach##1
 6. the person eating apple is the person drinking almond-milk##1
 7. the person drinking mirinda is the person eating peach##1
 8. the person eating papaya is on the right of the person eating peach##1
 9. the person drinking soy-milk is between the person drinking hot-chocolate and the person eating apple##2
10. the person drinking mirinda is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
