 4. the person drinking cola is between the person drinking sprite and the person eating peach##2
 5. the person eating apricot is the person drinking cola##1
 6. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
 7. the person eating cucumber is the person drinking tea##1
 8. the person eating papaya is the person eating papaya##1
 9. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person eating peas##1
10. the person eating papaya is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2    |     3     |       4       |      5      |    6     |    7     |
| Beverage   | almond-milk       | coffee | soy-milk      | tea | sprite       | cola | juice |
| Food       | lime | papaya    | plum | cucumber    | peas | apricot   | peach |

