.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-20::.
There 7 different types of food: asparagus, apple, garlic, avocado, spinach, banana, orange
The people have 7 different jobs:  designer, dressmaker, bartender, scientist, photographer, manager, fisherman
1. the person eating banana is on the left of the bartender##1
2. the photographer is in the middle##1
3. the person eating banana is on the far left##1
4. the person eating garlic is between the person eating avocado and the designer##2
5. the bartender is on the left of the person eating asparagus##1
6. the manager is on the left of the person eating spinach##1
7. the photographer is on the right of the scientist##1
8. the fisherman is between the person eating orange and the manager##2
9. the person eating orange is on the right of the scientist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |      2      |     3     |     4      |         5          |        6        |     7      |
| Food   | banana | apple    | asparagus | orange | avocado              | garlic      | spinach    |
| Job    | dressmaker | bartender | scientist  | photographer   | fisherman | manager | designer |

 